data.bio: Federal Special Agent in the FBI's BAU pursuing the world's most dangerous serial killers. I write romance novels and DBZ fan fic in my spare time.  My Larb Salad is to die for.
Legendary British King, One of the Nine Worthies, wielder of Excalibur, and destroyer of Saxons. Big fan of Bradley James' work. I specialize in cooking wild game
Northern Irish Actor from Belfast. I love wrinkling my forehead and wielding lightsabers. I will find you and I will feed you.
